com.idevicesinc.sweetblue

Class BleServer.ExchangeListener.ExchangeEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.utils.Event
      • com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.BleServer.ExchangeListener.ExchangeEvent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BleServer.IncomingListener.IncomingEvent, BleServer.OutgoingListener.OutgoingEvent
    Enclosing interface:
    BleServer.ExchangeListener

    public abstract static class BleServer.ExchangeListener.ExchangeEvent
extends Event
    Like BleServer.ExchangeListener, this class should not be used directly as this is just a base class to statically tie together BleServer.IncomingListener.IncomingEvent and BleServer.OutgoingListener.OutgoingEvent with a common API.

      • charUuid

        public final java.util.UUID charUuid()
        The UUID of the characteristic associated with this BleServer.ExchangeListener.ExchangeEvent. This will always be a valid UUID, even if target() is BleServer.ExchangeListener.Target.DESCRIPTOR.

      • descUuid

        public final java.util.UUID descUuid()
        The UUID of the descriptor associated with this BleServer.ExchangeListener.ExchangeEvent. If target() is BleServer.ExchangeListener.Target.CHARACTERISTIC then this will be referentially equal (i.e. you can use == to compare) to NON_APPLICABLE_UUID.

      • data_received

        public final byte[] data_received()
        The data received from the client if type() is BleServer.ExchangeListener.Type.isWrite(), otherwise an empty byte array. This is in contrast to BleServer.OutgoingListener.OutgoingEvent.data_sent() if type() is BleServer.ExchangeListener.Type.isRead().

      • requestId

        public final int requestId()
        The request id forwarded from the native stack. See various methods of BluetoothGattServerCallback for explanation. Not relevant if type() BleServer.ExchangeListener.Type.isNotificationOrIndication() is true.

      • offset

        public final int offset()
        The offset forwarded from the native stack. See various methods of BluetoothGattServerCallback for explanation. Not relevant if type() BleServer.ExchangeListener.Type.isNotificationOrIndication() is true.

      • responseNeeded

        public final boolean responseNeeded()
        Dictates whether a response is needed. Not relevant if type() BleServer.ExchangeListener.Type.isNotificationOrIndication() is true.
